<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .doc-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .doc-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .doc-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .swagger-color { color: #85ea2d; }
        .redoc-color { color: #8cc8ff; }
        .json-color { color: #ff6b6b; }
        .yaml-color { color: #ffd93d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                AmexingWeb API Documentation
            </h1>
            <p class="lead">
                Comprehensive documentation for the AmexingWeb PCI DSS compliant e-commerce platform API
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="badge bg-success me-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> PCI DSS Compliant
                </span>
                <span class="badge bg-info me-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Secure
                </span>
                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> High Performance
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card doc-card h-100 text-center p-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-code doc-icon swagger-color"></i>
                        <h3 class="card-title">Swagger UI Documentation</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Interactive API documentation with try-it-out functionality. 
                            Test endpoints directly from your browser.
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= apiDocsUrl %>" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                            Open Swagger UI
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card doc-card h-100 text-center p-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-book doc-icon redoc-color"></i>
                        <h3 class="card-title">ReDoc Documentation</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Beautiful, responsive documentation with detailed descriptions 
                            and examples for all API endpoints.
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= redocUrl %>" class="btn btn-info btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                            Open ReDoc
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card doc-card h-100 text-center p-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-alt doc-icon json-color"></i>
                        <h3 class="card-title">OpenAPI JSON</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Download the complete OpenAPI specification in JSON format 
                            for code generation and tooling.
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= specJsonUrl %>" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" download>
                            <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
                            Download JSON
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card doc-card h-100 text-center p-4">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-code doc-icon yaml-color"></i>
                        <h3 class="card-title">OpenAPI YAML</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Download the complete OpenAPI specification in YAML format 
                            for human-readable documentation.
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= specYamlUrl %>" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg" download>
                            <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
                            Download YAML
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h4 class="mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                            Getting Started
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-key text-warning"></i> Authentication</h5>
                                <p>This API uses session-based authentication. Include your session token in the <code>X-Parse-Session-Token</code> header.</p>
                                
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-success"></i> Security</h5>
                                <p>All endpoints enforce HTTPS in production and include comprehensive security headers for PCI DSS compliance.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt text-info"></i> Rate Limiting</h5>
                                <p>API endpoints are rate-limited to prevent abuse. Check response headers for rate limit information.</p>
                                
                                <h5><i class="fas fa-question-circle text-secondary"></i> Support</h5>
                                <p>For questions or support, please contact our development team or check our GitHub repository.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-4 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 AmexingWeb. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                Built with Express.js, Parse Server, and ❤️
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>